363, 157.0468, 160.2004, 159.2199, 160.9527, 162.9977, 162.8029, 161.1591, 159.7285, 159.7038, 159.3554, 159.2836, 158.3929, 156.7814, 158.0966, 157.3779, 157.3654, 158.6628, 159.7, 160.677, 162.1844, 161.8153, 161.6457, 162.8114, 162.938, 163.1762, 164.4356, 165.3101, 165.0512, 165.6685, 164.7391, 163.3209, 163.3075, 163.5465, 163.7781, 163.2665, 163.5432, 161.5103, 162.2973, 161.9017, 162.8584, 161.7879, 162.958, 163.8243, 163.0502, 163.55, 164.9803, 166.0683, 167.1634, 168.9016, 168.0046, 166.7088, 166.7807, 167.5508, 166.3859, 166.4723, 166.9306, 167.1882, 167.3161, 167.827, 168.8557, 168.6784, 169.5058, 168.0998, 169.1996, 169.8631, 170.7327, 170.3944, 170.9981, 170.0341, 169.5533, 169.4937, 170.554, 170.1565, 168.7815, 169.963, 169.8977, 170.7725, 170.1271, 171.1865, 170.6684, 170.0279, 169.2717, 169.5994, 170.0264, 169.7883, 169.1478, 168.62, 168.7502, 168.268, 169.7208, 169.5061, 169.9227, 170.8292, 170.4437, 170.5016, 169.5325, 168.9265, 169.0923, 168.0203, 168.5915, 170.0148, 168.9022, 168.8383, 169.7074, 168.9728, 169.7958, 168.2439, 167.8963, 168.6389, 166.8996, 165.5154, 166.7634, 166.8472, 166.0726, 167.2459, 166.1599, 165.5023, 166.0389, 166.1909, 166.4076, 166.4687, 166.4709, 165.1583, 165.7709, 166.5641, 165.92, 165.8555, 166.9087, 166.3429, 166.3093, 165.9662, 165.8561, 166.1405, 165.9342, 166.0995, 168.1642, 167.4546, 168.7376, 168.7459, 169.9584, 169.7699, 171.7451, 173.4669, 170.0418, 171.9487, 168.8317, 164.3763, 161.442, 168.0321, 162.2458, 162.6476, 160.6772, 158.9725, 158.7952, 154.9989, 153.1301, 151.8313, 151.5175, 151.3818, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>GTJA CTA 多因子回暖系列十四 -- 截面多因子组合</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>报告梳理了国泰君安期货 CTA 商品因子体系的六大类因子 (时序动量、截面动量、截面库存、截面仓单、期限结构、截面偏度), 展示了各因子在 2023 年 6-9 月的表现并与 CTA 私募产品净值做对比。本复现提取报告定义的全部因子类别, 在全品种商品期货上构建截面多因子模型。</p>\n<p>最终最优变体为三因子组合: <strong>截面偏度 (skew_120) + 期限结构 (ry_s40) + 仓单变化 (rcpt_chg_80)</strong>, 权重 40/40/20, 每 20 日换仓。截面偏度因子利用 120 日收益率偏度的截面排名, 做空高偏度品种 (上涨不对称、均值回归预期), 做多低偏度品种; 期限结构因子利用 40 日平滑展期收益率的截面排名, 做多 contango 品种 (正向展期); 仓单因子利用 80 日仓单变化率排名, 做空仓单增加的品种 (供给端压力)。三因子组合后信号更平滑、更稳健。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-16.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2644</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.36 / 1.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.68</td><td>1.61</td><td>1.47</td><td>1.19</td><td>0.99</td><td>1.73</td><td>1.9</td><td>0.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.85</span></td><td>0.35</td><td>1.48</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.85</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 120 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 120 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2646</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>35.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>偏度因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{skew}_{i,t} = \\text{Skewness}\\left(\\ln\\frac{P_{i,\\tau}}{P_{i,\\tau-1}}\\right)_{\\tau \\in [t-120, t]}</div>\n<p><strong>期限结构因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_s40}_{i,t} = \\frac{1}{40} \\sum_{\\tau=t-39}^{t} \\text{ry}_{i,\\tau}</div>\n<p><strong>仓单变化因子:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rcpt\\_chg80}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{receipt}_{i,t}}{\\text{receipt}_{i,t-80}} - 1</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = -0.4 \\cdot R(\\text{skew}_{i,t}) + 0.4 \\cdot R(\\text{ry\\_s40}_{i,t}) - 0.2 \\cdot R(\\text{rcpt\\_chg80}_{i,t})</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">R(\\cdot)</span> 为截面百分位排名映射到 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, 1]</span>。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>6 类因子全部实现, cs_skew_120 Sharpe 0.83 最优, term_struct_s40 紧随 (0.82)</td><td>实现所有因子类别 (tsmom/csmom/inventory/receipt/term_struct/skewness), 以截面排名+连续信号方式输出</td><td>偏度和期限结构因子表现突出, 动量和库存因子较弱</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>偏度+期限结构两因子是核心; turnover 0.56 偏高</td><td>1) 偏度窗口网格 [40-180]; 2) skew+ts 组合权重网格; 3) 加入 3 因子 (skew+ts+receipt)</td><td>Sharpe 提升到 1.09 (sk120_ts40 combo), turnover 降至 0.31, 3 因子组合也达 1.07</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>combo 信号稳健, 3 因子方向正确</td><td>1) 精细化 skew [100-150] x ts [30-50] 网格; 2) 3 因子组合网格 (receipt lookback [40-80]); 3) vol-target + IC gate</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.33</strong> (str_120_40_80), 回撤仅 -25.6%, 半样本检验 1.82/1.11 稳定</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R1 发现偏度因子出人意料地强 (Sharpe 0.83), 超过了报告重点强调的动量因子。R2 将偏度与期限结构组合后突破 1.0。R3 加入仓单因子 (80 日变化率) 形成三因子组合, 进一步提升至 1.33 并大幅压缩回撤。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货 (~56 个活跃品种), 依赖 ry/receipt 字段 (非空率 ~37%/23%)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20 天换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 与因子库 bohai carry 因子相关性 0.52 (边界冗余); 2023-2024 年表现较弱 (偏度信号在低波动环境效果打折)</li>\n<li><strong>NAV 终值 9.89x</strong>: 实际敞口较大 (年化波动率 0.78), 如需控制风险可使用 vol-target 版本</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>SKEW_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>120</code></td><td>rolling skewness lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>RY_SMOOTH</code></td><td><code>40</code></td><td>roll-yield smoothing window</td></tr><tr><td><code>RCPT_LB</code></td><td><code>80</code></td><td>receipt change-rate lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_SKEW</code></td><td><code>0.4</code></td><td>skewness weight (negated in combo)</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_TS</code></td><td><code>0.4</code></td><td>term-structure weight</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_RCPT</code></td><td><code>0.2</code></td><td>receipt weight (negated in combo)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.14s</li>\n</ul>"}